---

> ATGUI is a Simple Pythonic GUI Creation Library for all your Terminal needs!

# Installation

Get ATGUI by running these following Commands:

- For Stable Releases
```sh
pip install atgui
```

- For Development Releases
```sh
pip install git+https://github.com/x4raynixx/ATGUI
```

